sequenceDiagram
    participant LangGraph as LangGraph Workflow
    participant State as EngineeringState
    participant Specialists as Specialist Agents
    participant Implementers as Implementation Agents
    participant Validators as Validation Agents
    participant Workspace as Docker Workspace
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL

    LangGraph->>State: Initialize state<br/>(run_id, task, status=CREATED)
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint (CREATED)

    Note over LangGraph: CREATED Node
    LangGraph->>State: Set status=PREPARING_WORKSPACE
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint

    Note over LangGraph: PREPARING_WORKSPACE Node
    LangGraph->>Workspace: Create workspace container
    Workspace->>Workspace: Clone repository
    Workspace->>Workspace: Create run-specific branch
    Workspace-->>LangGraph: workspace_id, branch_name
    LangGraph->>State: Set workspace_id, workspace_branch
    LangGraph->>State: Set status=SCOUTING
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint

    Note over LangGraph: SCOUTING Node
    LangGraph->>Specialists: repo-scout agent
    Specialists->>Workspace: Read repository files
    Workspace-->>Specialists: File contents
    Specialists-->>LangGraph: RepositorySummary
    LangGraph->>State: Set repository_summary
    LangGraph->>State: Set status=PLANNING
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint

    Note over LangGraph: PLANNING Node
    LangGraph->>Specialists: skills-lead agent
    Specialists-->>LangGraph: SkillsLeadDecision<br/>(selected_agents)
    LangGraph->>Specialists: solution-planner agent
    Specialists-->>LangGraph: ImplementationPlan
    LangGraph->>State: Set selected_agents, implementation_plan
    LangGraph->>State: Set status=DESIGNING
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint

    Note over LangGraph: DESIGNING Node
    LangGraph->>Specialists: Design agent
    Specialists-->>LangGraph: DesignSpec
    LangGraph->>State: Set design_spec
    LangGraph->>State: Set status=IMPLEMENTING
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint

    Note over LangGraph: IMPLEMENTING Node
    par Parallel Implementation
        LangGraph->>Implementers: Go developer agent
        Implementers->>Workspace: Write/patch files
        Implementers->>Workspace: Run git diff
        Implementers-->>LangGraph: ImplementationResult
    and
        LangGraph->>Implementers: Angular developer agent
        Implementers->>Workspace: Write/patch files
        Implementers->>Workspace: Run git diff
        Implementers-->>LangGraph: ImplementationResult
    and
        LangGraph->>Implementers: DevOps developer agent
        Implementers->>Workspace: Write/patch files
        Implementers->>Workspace: Run git diff
        Implementers-->>LangGraph: ImplementationResult
    end
    LangGraph->>State: Set implementation_results, code_diff
    LangGraph->>State: Set status=TESTING
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint

    Note over LangGraph: TESTING Node
    LangGraph->>Validators: Backend test engineer
    Validators->>Workspace: Run tests (allowlist)
    Workspace-->>Validators: Test output
    Validators-->>LangGraph: TestResult
    LangGraph->>Validators: Angular test engineer
    Validators->>Workspace: Run tests (allowlist)
    Workspace-->>Validators: Test output
    Validators-->>LangGraph: TestResult
    LangGraph->>State: Set test_results
    LangGraph->>State: Set status=REVIEWING
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint

    Note over LangGraph: REVIEWING Node
    LangGraph->>Validators: Code reviewer agent
    Validators-->>LangGraph: ReviewResult<br/>(findings with severity)
    LangGraph->>State: Set review_results
    LangGraph->>State: Set status=VERIFYING
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint

    Note over LangGraph: VERIFYING Node
    LangGraph->>Validators: Completion verifier agent
    Validators-->>LangGraph: VerificationResult<br/>(criteria results)
    LangGraph->>State: Set verification_results

    alt Verification passed
        LangGraph->>State: Set status=COMPLETED
        LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint (COMPLETED)
    else Verification failed & repair_count < max
        LangGraph->>State: Set status=REPAIRING<br/>increment repair_count
        LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint (REPAIRING)
        Note over LangGraph: REPAIRING Node
        LangGraph->>State: Set status=IMPLEMENTING
        LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint
    else Verification failed & repair_count >= max
        LangGraph->>State: Set status=FAILED
        LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint (FAILED)
    end

    Note over LangGraph: Terminal State Reached
    LangGraph->>Workspace: Cleanup workspace
    Workspace->>Workspace: Remove container & volume
